GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_CoreWorkflows> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_CoreWorkflows> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#CoreWorkflows> ;
    narr:childCount "43"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "9ae2f624249375a3abbce1282b453198c1b97e9a" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers the operational patterns aswritten runs on. The flagship is the session-to-document arc: [Interview → Save → Draft → Annotate](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_InterviewSaveDraftAnnotatePattern), grounded by [save before drafting](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SaveBeforeDrafting), disciplined by [one question at a time](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_OneQuestionAtATime), and generalized as a [replicable pattern for any strategic document](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_SessionPatternReplicable). The interview discipline is sharpened by [corrections-over-hypotheses](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_InterviewBeforeSynthesis): user corrections reveal thinking not yet in collective memory and are treated as more valuable than the AI's initial hypotheses. Review is treated as recursion — [review is just another remember](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ReviewLoopIsRemember), with [Scarlet's canonical statement](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ReviewIsRememberQuote) as the anchor. A dated March 26 simplification collapses standalone tools into on-demand local skills: [Stories](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_StoriesRemoved), [Notifications](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_NotificationsRemoved), [Refract/Registry](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_RefractRegistryRemoved), and [Memories/Source](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_MemoriesSourceToolRemoved) all removed, keeping only the [feedback/help tool above the line](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_FeedbackHelpAboveLine). The pipeline is described in two overlapping accounts — a [six-step commit-to-PR flow](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_PipelineSteps) and a [five-step review-as-optometrist flow](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_Pipeline). Review-comparison corrections insist on [baseline-first](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_BaselineFirst), [labeled shift intent](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_LabelShiftIntent), and [small comparison chunks](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_ComparisonScale). Sales and consulting flows — [two-call structure](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_TwoCallStructure), [influence-first](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_InfluenceSales), [two-week engagement](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Workflow_ConsultingEngagement) — sit alongside the core write-path patterns.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CollaborativeMemory> ;
